        {
            "title": "CFTC考慮阻止芝商所推出全天候原油期貨合約",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sf_LJmQEq7lqI70i04l5KQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED9U19I_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 據彭博社報道，消息人士透露，美國商品期貨交易委員會（CFTC）正在評估是否應阻止芝加哥商品交易所集團（CME Group）推出全天候原油期貨合約的計劃，一名熟悉此事的監管機構高級官員證實了相關討論的存在。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">芝商所於上週四宣布，計劃針對特定原油及黃金期貨合約推出每週七天、每天24小時的全天候交易服務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報道，監管機構擔憂，原油期貨的持續交易可能在地緣政治局勢緊張及市場壓力加劇期間，進一步放大市場波動性。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-698f55fd-0cf7-3e0b-a458-adb0667d3201-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">擬推出的原油合約規模為芝商所現有微型WTI期貨合約的十分之一，預計於8月30日正式上市，惟須待監管機構批准。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">芝商所亦計劃於7月26日啟動其1盎司黃金期貨合約的全天候交易。上述兩款產品均需經CFTC審核後方可推出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">芝商所發言人拒絕就相關報道置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此事發生於一週前，芝商所首席執行官泰瑞·達菲（Terry Duffy）就CFTC批准永續加密貨幣期貨合約（俗稱「永續合約」或「perps」）交易一事表達了關切。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CFTC表示，其對永續期貨申請採取逐案審查的方式，並指出某些資產可能並不適合此類產品結構。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">永續期貨在加密貨幣市場中被廣泛使用，亦是Hyperliquid平台的主要交易工具。受伊朗與以色列衝突引發的市場波動影響，該平台上與原油掛鉤產品的交易量近期顯著上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報道還指出，芝商所與洲際交易所（Intercontinental Exchange）此前均已呼籲監管機構，對提供類似產品的未受監管交易平台加強審查。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/cftc%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E8%8A%9D%E5%95%86%E6%89%80%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E5%85%A8%E5%A4%A9%E5%80%99%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E6%9C%9F%E8%B2%A8%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84-013543132.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-06-13 09:55:37",
